content: Hi <@1278118222876639326> Thanks for reaching out! It looks like you are fully onboarded. There's a new channel called <#1287795589655822397> that has lots of good information. Thank you so much for coming back!
What do the different colors stand for? Where do I find the scripted responses?

There are three STW accounts now; you may need to sign up for pink and green since you were onboarded a while ago. Those links should still be in the <#1245442408305393675> channel. The scripted responses are in the campaigns themselves, as replies. We are not sending out the texts, only doing replies.
